WEBVTT

00:05:29.693 --> 00:05:32.470
from the Underground station
you see on the bottom right.

00:05:32.805 --> 00:05:34.104
So you see the desire path.

00:05:34.128 --> 00:05:36.942
If we just wind the clock
back a few years,

00:05:36.966 --> 00:05:39.163
when the stadium was being constructed,

00:05:39.187 --> 00:05:40.746
there is no desire path.

00:05:41.797 --> 00:05:45.943
So our job is to watch
for these desire paths emerging,

00:05:46.567 --> 00:05:48.331
and, where appropriate, pave them,

00:05:48.975 --> 00:05:50.530
as someone did here.

00:05:51.191 --> 00:05:52.839
Someone installed a barrier,

00:05:54.076 --> 00:05:57.296
people started walking across
and round the bottom as you see,

00:05:57.320 --> 00:05:58.518
and they paved it.

00:05:58.542 --> 00:06:00.122
(Laughter)